                     <interp inst="t18570817-896-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>Stealing 3 tame fowls, price 8<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18570817-name-438" type="victimName">
